WEBVTT

1
01:26:11.210 --> 01:26:14.980 
但我妈妈仍然想为他在家办一场葬礼
My mother still chose to have a memorial for him back home.

2
01:26:14.980 --> 01:26:18.350 
让我们安葬詹姆斯·L·巴斯比的遗体
Let us commit James L. Busbee's body to the ground,

3
01:26:18.350 --> 01:26:21.650 
尘归尘
earth to earth, ashes to ashes,

4
01:26:21.660 --> 01:26:23.960 
土归土
dust to dust,

5
01:26:23.960 --> 01:26:26.890 
让往生者安宁
in the sure and certain hope

6
01:26:26.900 --> 01:26:30.460 
让在世者重获解脱
of the resurrection to eternal life.

7
01:26:30.470 --> 01:26:35.030 
以圣父  圣子
In the name of the Father and of the Son

8
01:26:35.040 --> 01:26:38.070 
以及圣灵之名  阿门
and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.

